name: Soros
additional_notices: No active trades are found for this coin. Please submit a ticket at %{link} if you think this is an error.

description.en:
What is the project about?
A new generation of blockchain: the evolution of ethereum and BSC has arrived. Lower fees and POA (Proof of Authority). Now unleash your full potential in contracts on the Soros chain.

What makes your project unique?
Lower fees, and genuine community for education and dapps development

History of your project.


What’s next for your project?
Dapps, Financial use, Institutional Nodes and validators, education

What can your token be used for?
Validators nodes, Use in marketplaces, mint NFTs, Stake gas
